object.script:
local gB, gN, sB, sN, pN, pB = input.getBool, input.getNumber, output.setBool, output.setNumber, property.getNumber, property.getBool
local labels = {{"Axis 1 [a]/[d] Sensitivity (%)", "Axis 2 [w]/[s] Sensitivity (%)", "Axis 3 [left]/[right] Sensitivity (%)", "Axis 4 [up]/[down] Sensitivity (%)"}, {"Axis 1 [a]/[d] Mode", "Axis 2 [w]/[s] Mode", "Axis 3 [left]/[right] Mode", "Axis 4 [up]/[down] Mode"}, {"Hotkey 1", "Hotkey 2", "Hotkey 3", "Hotkey 4", "Hotkey 5", "Hotkey 6", "Trigger"}} local properties = {{0, 0, 0, 0}, {false, false, false, false}, {false, false, false, false, false, false, false}} local init = true
local deltas = {0, 0, 0, 0} local axes = {0, 0, 0, 0} local hotkeys = {{false, false, false, false, false, false, false}, {false, false, false, false, false, false, false}} local active = false
function onTick() if init then for i = 1, 4 do properties[1][i] = pN(labels[1][i]) / 100 properties[2][i] = pB(labels[2][i]) end for i = 1, 7 do properties[3][i] = pB(labels[3][i]) end init = false end for i = 1, 7 do if properties[3][i] and hotkeys[1][i] then hotkeys[1][i] = false end if gB(32) then local hotkey = gB(i > 6 and 31 or i) if properties[3][i] then if not active then hotkeys[2][i] = hotkey elseif hotkey ~= hotkeys[2][i] then hotkeys[2][i] = hotkey hotkeys[1][i] = true end else if not active then hotkeys[2][i] = hotkey elseif hotkey ~= hotkeys[2][i] then hotkeys[2][i] = hotkey hotkeys[1][i] = not hotkeys[1][i] end end end sB(i > 6 and 31 or i, hotkeys[1][i]) end active = gB(32) sB(32, gB(32)) for i = 1, 4 do local axis = gN(i) local delta = axis - deltas[i] deltas[i] = axis if (axis > 0 and delta > 0) or (axis < 0 and delta > 0.01) or axis > 0.999 then axes[i] = lerp(axes[i], 1, properties[1][i]) sN(i, axes[i]) elseif (axis < 0 and delta < 0) or (axis > 0 and delta < -0.01) or axis < -0.999 then axes[i] = lerp(axes[i], -1, properties[1][i]) sN(i, axes[i]) elseif not properties[2][i] then axes[i] = lerp(axes[i], 0, properties[1][i]) sN(i, axes[i]) end end end
function lerp(a,b,t) return a + (b-a) * t * t end
